Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,~Dialogue~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.11,Default,Armed Disciplinary Officer,0,0,0,,西园寺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.36,Default,Armed Disciplinary Officer,0,0,0,,挟持女生作人质  也太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.91,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,卑鄙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:25.88,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,这对我来说可是称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.44,Default,Saionji,1200,0,0,,积极  健康  向上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:32.38,Default,Saionji,1200,0,0,,那种事情机器人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:35.99,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,我要卑鄙  下流  无情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.19,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,为了目的不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.76,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,因为我是遵从黑暗武士道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.23,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.58,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,像是 20 世纪的动画一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:58.44,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,他真的是主人公吗？ 不是反派？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.01,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,他就是主人公！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.76,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,田  田口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:09.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,这个主人公他偷拐抢骗  恣意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:15.25,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,更可怕的是  他从来不会因此受到报应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.51,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,这是在正当化有违道德的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.49,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,比色情血腥更加危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.27,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,这个作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:30.84,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,现在在孩子中非常有影响力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:37.40,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,让我们来改变现状吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:43.13,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,让这邪典动画彻底消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.56,Default,Wholesome Members,0,0,0,,彻底消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:23.72,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,距目的地还剩 20 分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.82,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,因为我的父母思想非常守旧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:31.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,所以我未曾能够尽情享受虚拟娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.02,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我不想让我的孩子也经历同样的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.24,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,价值观是随时代变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.01,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,而不是父母硬加给孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:51.00,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我希望孩子能够随好奇心驱使  去探索尝试各种事物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.68,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我真是怀着这样的想法把他们养大的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.10,Default,Taguchi's Wife,0,0,0,,该吃饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.71,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,不管妇女儿童  挡我者死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.76,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,0,0,,挡我者死！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.04,Default,Taguchi Wife,0,0,0,,喂  不要这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.83,Default,Taguchi Wife,0,0,0,,该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.55,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,不想被捕食就快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.06,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,0,0,,吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:18.17,Default,Taguchi Son,900,0,0,,黑暗  黑暗  黑暗  黑暗  黑暗武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.82,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,800,0,,黑暗武士道  西园寺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:26.45,Top - s,Kids,0,0,0,,黑暗  黑暗  黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.93,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,感觉  烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:30.91,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,『黑暗武士道』那种邪典动画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.34,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,绝不能放放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:38.17,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,既然作品是如此  创作者估计也不是善茬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.17,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,对本站发出的电话采访请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.68,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,『黑暗武士道』的导演小山田茄子如此回应道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.80,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,「有意见就当面跟我说」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.18,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,「但要做好以死相博的准备」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,嗯  所以怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.65,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你们想要怎么处理我的动画？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.89,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我说啊  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.94,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你做的是给小孩子看的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.92,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,希望你能够保守最基本的伦理底线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.61,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,什么伦理底线？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.16,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,那是你们画的线吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.87,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,您当然是有创作自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,但是我们也有权发声…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.54,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.87,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,撒尿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.12,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,我还以为动画是要很多人才能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.78,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,没想到他一个人就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.23,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,这就是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.57,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,和过去不同  现在光靠一个人就能随意创作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:46.20,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,所以审查才会失效  导致各种邪典的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:50.49,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,画面的魅力很强  对于儿童来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.70,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.93,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.22,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是贫血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.97,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的生活习惯太不健康了  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.76,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,又受你照顾了  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:14.98,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:19.34,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,到这里来就能吃到营养代餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我们的只是医疗用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,虽然难吃  但比外面卖的便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.32,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,不惜搞坏身体  你究竟在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.83,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,为什么不做点更有意义的作品呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.01,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我只是在做想做的作品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.83,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你是不会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.09,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:47.56,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,如果社会继续迎合你们这样的好好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.85,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,坏事会不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.25,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,这个国家的犯罪率每年都在降低  正…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.84,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.48,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我是说会有更多的事会被认定为「恶」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.93,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,开车就是一个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.63,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,现在自己开车的人  都会被骂做是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,总有一天  只要身为人类就会称为恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.29,Default,Wholesome B,0,0,0,,他在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.36,Default,Wholesome B,0,0,0,,就好像他根本没做坏事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,他要是不创作邪恶的题材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.73,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,就没法在这个 AI 社会表现自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:38.63,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,因为那种肯定邪恶的故事  是 AI 无法想象出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,在伦理上来讲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.47,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:46.00,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,嗯  「儿童健康什么什么」的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.74,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,话说医生  我现在是病人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.32,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,给我营养代餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.59,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,天真  太傻白甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.70,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,比糖尿病大叔的尿还要甜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:08.92,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,就凭这种攻击也想要阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.01,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.81,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,你的玩具挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.77,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,武装风纪委员长  这太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.83,Default,Sainoji,0,0,0,,好了  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.66,Default,Sainoji,0,0,0,,我会拼上性命和你决斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.30,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,等等  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.86,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,今天可不会让你跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.71,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我没跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.05,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,须堂医生叫我过去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.04,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我只是去做定期体检…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.31,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我可是收集到了这么多签名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.08,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你给我看也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.42,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,去拿给政府什么的看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.41,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,看到这么一叠文件  你就不会良心不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.55,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小山田先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.43,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:26.92,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,你小子  撞了人就这么无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.42,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.42,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,赔钱啊  杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.42,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你  你们说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.69,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,是想要恐吓大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.91,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,在这种大街上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.95,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你想要毁掉自己的人生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.72,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,快住手  不要刺激他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.40,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,就是因为你正面描绘不良行为  这种人才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.38,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.41,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你们赢了  就算了吧  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.73,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,大叔你是他的同伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.22,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.67,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,你也给我赔钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.47,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,交  交叉迎击？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.15,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,抱歉  不由得就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:38.74,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,不要让我滥用我赖以吃饭的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.30,Default,Punk B,0,0,0,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.36,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.96,Default,Punk B,0,0,0,,喂… 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.40,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,他也是仿生人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.46,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,死是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.92,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.66,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我会拼上性命和你决斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.27,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,治疗结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.53,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.53,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:26.61,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我听护士说你不打算报警  你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.71,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,只是几个见血就吓跑了的小人物罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.17,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你为什么保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.43,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,大反派也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.42,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,但我也喜欢描绘今天这样的小恶党
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.52,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小恶党!? 他可是割伤了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.68,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你会这么想也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.00,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,如果我们就像这样  不断缩小邪恶的阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.68,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,等到完全消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.69,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,剩下的就不能再称之为人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.24,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,而是  曾是人类的某种事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.70,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,西园寺是个坏蛋  但有时也是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.26,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,我就是喜欢这种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.71,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,好弱  好弱鸡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.21,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,明  明明把我作为肉盾的话  你就能轻松取胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.23,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.19,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.09,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,其实是个好人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.70,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,我可是遵从黑暗武士道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.11,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教书育人是人类非常重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,就算产业 AI 有多发达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:43.24,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也应当由人类型智慧来主导现场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:48.74,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,小学是儿童树立自我的重要时期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.32,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,产业 AI 的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.75,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,可能会导致感情细腻的儿童偏离人性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:13:01.84,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,属于人类的  源于人类的  为人类服务的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.13,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,这是本校的教育政策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.94,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,所以  你真的要去那里工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.85,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,毕竟拿到内定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.73,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.49,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,那里在业界的风评很差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.26,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我听说那里因为歧视仿生人上过新闻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.27,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但那是很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,现在负责管理的人已经换了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.77,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,现在他们非常重视透明度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.02,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,还会将教室实时直播给家长们什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.28,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,这真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.75,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,隐私方面什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.45,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,这没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.75,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,因为不是自家的孩子都会打上马赛克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.97,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,打马赛克的时是使用的 AI 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.97,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,这方针有点不太对头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.07,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,总之似乎就是不使用 AI 参与授课就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教室里也不设机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.11,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,在这个时代还这么搞  我真是搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.11,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.02,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,实话说我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.91,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但其他的学校全都应聘失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.16,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,虽说也可以给你数字版的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.21,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,但总之你好好看一遍这本手册
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.72,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,学校内的情况  家长全都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.72,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,大家都是为了这份安心  才选择的本校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:32.21,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,所以要注意对待学生的方法  不要引来投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.56,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.79,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,回答不可以这么随便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.30,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是  是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,在这个国家的小学和初中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.91,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,很多都在教室里设置得有机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.08,Default,Student A,0,0,0,,喂  能教我这道题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.62,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,好的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.60,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,四则运算呢  要先…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.99,Default,Student B,1200,0,0,,你真敢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.38,Default,Student C,0,0,0,,是你的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.11,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,不可以打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.33,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,不可以打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.34,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,机器人在各种场合都非常有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:09.31,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,让 AI 做教育顾问也是很常见的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:14.18,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,但是  我也不能为了他一个人降低课程的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:20.08,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,自尊心和理解度是成正相关的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.63,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,不如敞开胸怀好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.96,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,不再以教师和学生的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:29.26,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,而是以朋友的身份重新建立关系怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.45,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,嗯  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:38.32,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,有很多教师照本宣科地按照 AI 的指示来教育学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.71,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,我想要他成为一个有人性的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.46,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,他拥有着世界独一无二的宝贵个性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.94,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,这是没法托付给量产型的产业 AI 的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,如果说家长相信人类和仿生人教师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.34,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,事实也并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:10.44,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,今天不上课  所以没有直播  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.86,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,好  好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.73,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,你的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.37,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.17,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,那就开始模拟课程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.05,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.41,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,各位同学  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.42,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,太早了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.02,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,班会还有 30 秒才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.60,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,要是之后还有学生进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.57,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,就会觉得自己迟到了  从而感到一种疏远感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.52,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我只是打了个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.23,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,班会还没有开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.11,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.61,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,以前有过投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:46.60,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.75,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,你要在预订时间的前后三秒内进入教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.07,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,给你的手册上也写得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.53,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,在明天前把它给记牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.49,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,你的回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.19,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.51,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,总之就是规矩繁多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.92,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,全是不准做这  不准做那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.43,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,像是必须用姓加「同学」来称呼孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,还要格外注意不能差别对待学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.33,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,父母监视得严吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.30,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,看得挺严的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.46,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我这就已经收到 3 次投诉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.70,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:45.83,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,二年级给大家带来的「幸福快乐舞蹈」到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.39,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,接下来是三年级给大家带来的虚拟叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.96,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,「大大大大金字塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:59.12,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,您看  孩子们开始精神同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.89,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,请看您植入物的 AR 画面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.98,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,孩子们的分身浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:15.49,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,现在  同学们的心念合一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.55,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,组成了大大的金字塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.31,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,虚拟叠罗汉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.10,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也算是运动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:33.00,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,这是我校特有的活动  广受家长们的好评
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.51,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,自然  这么做不会受伤  而且更重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.10,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,在家长自己的 AR 世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.41,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,都看到的是自己孩子在顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.64,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,看到自己的孩子是最受瞩目的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.65,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,所以家长们都非常满意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:55.81,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,建立在这种利害关系上  处处受限的「公平」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.92,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.86,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,这份公平真的有人性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:05.75,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,这所学校  真的有人性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:12.14,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,在监视中  教师们都害怕与学生交流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.94,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,只会进行机械化的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,不对问题儿童生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也不去陪伴帮助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.29,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,只是默默地将其劝退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:30.66,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我做教师不是为了来做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.94,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,喂  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.69,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.31,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.45,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,我得了特等奖！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.79,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:52.54,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,都是因为老师您叫我投稿  才会有今天！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.29,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,谢谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,我听教导主任说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.60,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,说是你请书法社的学生喝了饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.79,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,因为大西同学得了特等奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我才约好给他一点奖励…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.59,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,天气也很热…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.36,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,你还没理解我们的政策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,这是个很严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.70,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,有什么大不了的嘛  不就一杯饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,这才是人性化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.09,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,不要假扮人类  给别人添麻烦啊  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.36,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教师不是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.38,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是拥有着缺点和偏见的人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.61,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我本想着… 哪怕为了学生  也要坚持教完一年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.77,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是… 他们对待我的态度越来越差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.37,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我可以给你开一些药物治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:18.13,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但改变环境是最好的良药
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.28,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,从学校辞职差不多一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:31.68,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我开始在一家特殊教育机构帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.51,Default,Perm,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:34.58,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.06,Default,Toshiki,0,0,0,,不公平  怎么只给洋同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:41.65,Default,Perm,0,0,0,,等俊树同学你下次考出好成绩  我就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.39,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,他虽是看护机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:48.34,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,但他的 AI 是在学校里训练的  所以很擅长看顾儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.66,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,无法融入学校的儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.44,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,害怕成年人的儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.68,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,各种各样的儿童都会来我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:04.62,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,你的经验一定也能在这里派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:11.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,不知道家长们对帕玛同学是什么看法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.57,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,大家都说他是专业看护员  所以值得信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.56,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,不过在你听来  可能是十分讽刺
